messages.message:
Hi all — just did a pass of open PRs that haven’t had activity in over 1 month and labeled them all as “Stale”. I am going to close those PRs tomorrow by 8pm PST unless you remove the label and change it to “WIP” or another meaningful “i’m still working on this label”

Here is the current list of “Stale” PRs: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pulls?utf8=%E2%9C%93&q=is%3Apr+is%3Aopen+label%3Astale
